Getting Started Easy

Display the text "Welcome to the world of Web development" on the screen 
Acceptance Criteria: - The text should be inside the < code > div < /code> tag. - 
Add id=< code>text< /code> for the div tag.

Output Format

The text should be inside the < div> tag.
Add id="text" for the internal < div> tag.
Constraints

The HTML should enclosed in a < div> tag.

CODE
<!-- Write your HTML Code here  -->
<code>
    <div id="text">
        Welcome to the world of Web development
    </div>
</code>
